<%
// Brookings Crane Services
%>

<!-- Page Header -->
<section class="page-header" style="background-image: url('/images/port-orford.jpg');">
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Crane Tree Removal in Brookings, OR</h1>
        <p>Professional Crane Assisted Tree Service</p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Main Content -->
<section class="area-service-content section-padding">
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Intro with Image -->
        <div class="service-intro">
            <div class="intro-text">
                <p>JT & Sons Tree Service LLC provides safe and professional crane tree removal in Brookings, OR and surrounding areas. Some tree removals require specialized equipment due to tree size, location, or nearby structures. Our crane assisted tree services allow us to safely remove large or hazardous trees while protecting your home, property, and landscape.</p>
                <p>With over 30 years of experience, we have the knowledge and equipment to safely perform large tree removals, difficult tree removals, and crane-assisted tree trimming.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="intro-image">
                <img src="/images/bbroking.jpg" alt="Crane Service in Brookings" class="rounded-image">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Services List -->
        <div class="content-container">
            <h2>When Crane Tree Services Are Needed:</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Large tree removal</li>
                <li>Trees near homes or structures</li>
                <li>Difficult access tree removal</li>
                <li>Storm-damaged trees</li>
                <li>Emergency tree removal</li>
            </ul>
            <p>If you're looking for crane tree removal in Brookings OR, our experienced team is ready to help.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact Info -->
        <div class="contact-info-box">
            <h3>Call today for a free estimate</h3>
            <p>
                <i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i> Office: <a href="tel:<%= sitePhone %>"><%= sitePhone %></a><br>
                <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i> Cell/Text: <a href="tel:<%= siteCell %>"><%= siteCell %></a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>